      ******************************************************************
      * VIAP0021 - VALIDA SE UM DETERMINADO ANO E BISSEXTO             *
      ******************************************************************
       VIAP0021-VAL-BIS.
      *
           DIVIDE VIAW0021-ANO BY 4     GIVING VIAW0021-QUOCIENTE
                                        REMAINDER VIAW0021-VAR1.
           DIVIDE VIAW0021-ANO BY 100   GIVING VIAW0021-QUOCIENTE
                                        REMAINDER VIAW0021-VAR2.
           DIVIDE VIAW0021-ANO BY 400   GIVING VIAW0021-QUOCIENTE
                                        REMAINDER VIAW0021-VAR3.
           IF ( VIAW0021-VAR1     EQUAL ZEROS   AND
                VIAW0021-VAR2 NOT EQUAL ZEROS ) OR
              VIAW0021-VAR3 EQUAL ZEROS
              MOVE 'S'                     TO VIAW0021-IBISSEXTO
           ELSE
              MOVE 'N'                     TO VIAW0021-IBISSEXTO
           END-IF.
      *
       VIAP0021-VAL-BIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
